# Emma's Portfolio

## Quick Start

1. Install dependencies  
   `npm install`

2. Start the dev server  
   `npm run dev`

3. Edit content:
   - Home/Contact: Edit `src/pages/Home.jsx`, `src/pages/Contact.jsx`
   - Blog posts: Add markdown files to `src/content/academic/` or `src/content/personal/`
   - Images/videos: Add to `public/media/` and reference in markdown frontmatter as `media: "/media/filename.jpg"`

4. To change resume or links, update `public/resume.pdf` and `src/pages/Contact.jsx`.

---

## Deployment

You can deploy to [Vercel](https://vercel.com/), [Netlify](https://www.netlify.com/), or [GitHub Pages](https://vitejs.dev/guide/static-deploy.html).

---

## Color Palette

- Soft White: #FAFAFA
- Light Taupe: #ECE9E6
- Warm Gray: #B6B1A9
- Deep Charcoal: #3A3A3A
- Gold Accent: #D4AF37

